  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA258-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu tōḻi ceṟippaṟivuṟīiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante informed of confinement.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA258">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            palpūṅ kāṉaṟ pakaṟkuṟi marīic</l>
<l>            celval koṇka ceṟittaṉaḷ yāyē</l>
<l>            katirkāl vempak kalkāy ñāyiṟṟut</l>
<l>            tiruvuṭai viyaṉakar varuvirun tayarmār</l>
<l>            poṟṟoṭi makaḷir puṟaṅkaṭai yukutta </l>
<l>            kokkukir nimiraṉ mānti yeṟpaṭa</l>
<l>            vakalaṅ kāṭi yacainiḻaṟ kuvitta</l>
<l>            pacciṟāk kavarnta pacuṅkaṭ kākkai</l>
<l>            tūṅkal vaṅkattuk kūmpiṟ cēkku</l>
<l>            maruṅkūrp paṭṭiṉat taṉṉaviva </l>
<l>            ṇeruṅkē relvaḷai yōṭuva kaṇṭē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Having come to the meeting-place at midday, in the many-flowered seashore grove, I go,</l> 
<l>[back], man from the sea.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Mother has confined [her],</l>
<l rend="indent4">seeing the tight beautiful bright bangles slip down</l>
<l rend="indent4">from her [beautiful] as Maruṅkūrppaṭṭiṉam<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">maruṅkūr paṭṭiṉam</term>: or "as <term xml:lang="ta">Paṭṭiṉam</term>, the village by the side".</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent2">where the green-eyed crow,</l>
<l rend="indent">that had fed on the boiled rice [with grains long] as crane’s nails<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">kokku ukir nimiral</term>: thus T.V.G.’s explanation for this strange description: long rice is of a superior quality.</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent3">dropped outside by women with golden bracelets,</l>
<l rend="indent4">while the rich wide mansion is engaged in the coming feast,</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the sun hot on the stones, while the foot of [its] rays scorches,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and], when the light set, had seized the fresh prawn</l>
<l rend="indent3">heaped in the moving shade of the wide bazaar,</l>
<l rend="indent3">dwells on the mast of a ship in suspension.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
